These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, trike, quad-bike, subway
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, western, mystery, documentary
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, electrician, musician, project-manager
There are 4 different nationalities: german, pakistani, russian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rat, horse, goldfish
 1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 2. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 3. the musician is on the right of the electrician##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 8. the project-manager is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 9. the person driving the trike is the person watching mystery movies##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the russian##5
11. the german is somewhere to the right of the turkish##5
12. the musician is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
13. the pakistani is on the right of the electrician##1
14. the turkish is on the far left##1
15. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |       3       |        4        |
| Transport      | subway    | quad-bike        | trike | bus     |
| Movie-Genre          | thriller    | western  | mystery     | documentary          |
| Job           | electrician | musician     | dressmaker    | project-manager |
| Nationality   | turkish     | pakistani    | russian       | german          |
| Pet         | guinea-pig  | horse | rat       | goldfish         |

