.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-5-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, soy-milk, water
City: prague, hannover, san-francisco, nizza
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, magic-tricks, photography, video-games
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, lilac, ivory, amber
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, electronic, punk, house
 1. the fan of house is the person who likes amber##1
 2. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
 5. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
 8. the fan of jazz is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lilac##5
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to hannover##5
11. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
12. the person who likes apricot is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the fan of jazz##2
13. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
14. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |      2      |      3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | 7up        | soy-milk    | water        | milk         |
| City       | san-francisco   | hannover      | nizza       | prague        |
| Hobby      | card-games | photography | video-games  | magic-tricks |
| Color        | amber  | lilac   | apricot   | ivory     |
| Music-Genre      | house | jazz    | punk | electronic       |

