 3. the person drinking bolivarade is on the left of the scientist##1
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 5. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
 6. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
 7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person drinking bolivarade and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the security-guard##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
11. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
12. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
13. the journalist is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
