 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
 9. the musician is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
10. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
11. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
12. the person who likes amber is the fan of jazz##1
13. the fan of house is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
14. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
