 1. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the prince-smoker##2
 3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the mexican##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 5. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who growspoppy##1
 8. the argentine is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 9. the person who growsrose is the polish##1
10. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
11. the prince-smoker is in an even position##4
12. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
13. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
14. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
